room_title: Escape room "Sabotage" by Train Escape in Birmingham
room_description: Can you go deep behind enemy territory and stop a missile strike which endangers the safety of the entire world? Your elite team has infiltrated the enemies' train. There are 60 minutes before launch, you need to break into the locomotive control center and prevent it, or the consequence will be catastrophic. You can not leave the room the same way you entered or you will be apprehended by the enemy! Your country is counting on you!
